    "canonical_statement": "In networks with strongly heterogeneous couplings, global synchronization is suppressed unless the largest coupling pairs represent a significant fraction of total coupling. Planetary spins illustrate this: the Jupiter--Saturn pair dominates, so cluster dynamics should be analyzed in subsets rather than globally.",
